[navigation-shell] 5. Property detail tabs

Add the per-property tab system (design D6 — nested routes per tab).

- New <PropertyTabs> component: underline-style strip, horizontally
  scrollable on mobile when labels overflow, active state derived from
  the URL via usePathname. Slugs are part of the public URL contract —
  renaming requires a migration.
- New layout at /app/bolig/[id]/layout.tsx renders the tab strip and
  slots the active tab's page below it.
- /app/bolig/[id]/page.tsx redirects to ./oversikt by default
  (spec: "Default redirect to Oversikt").
- Five tab pages stubbed (oversikt, min-vurdering, sammenligning,
  kommentarer, notater), each with a TODO referencing the owning
  capability (properties / scoring / comparison).

